ly: MingLiU; mso-bidi-font-family: MingLiU\">香港四星酒店</span></a></span><span lang=\"ZH-TW\" style=\"font-family: MingLiU; color: black; mso-bidi-font-family: MingLiU\">，设有各种休闲与会议设施，合适不同须要的旅客入住。酒店附近红?港铁站，位於九龙市核心，徒步数分钟更可直达香港体育馆丶尖沙咀东部及香港迷信馆，交通四通八达，是香港游览的幻想住宿抉择。请即登录官方网站查问房价及预订。</span></font><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: MingLiU; color: black; mso-bidi-font-family: MingLiU\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p>	&nbsp;</p> ','0','');");
E_D("replace into `phome_ecms_infotmp_news` values('5272','10','http://www.baikezsw.com/dililvyou/4601.html','0','2016-01-18 16:01:12','1','admin','1453104072','','奢华客房','2016-01-18 16:01:12','','','','','','				  	<!--ad开始-->		<!--ad结束-->	<article class=\"post-22142 post type-post status-publish format-standard has-post-thumbnail hentry category-ps-skill category-colour_mixing_tutorials tag-kuler tag-colour_mixing post-listing\">			<div class=\"post-inner\">				<h2 class=\"post-title entry-title\">奢华客房</h2>										<div class=\"entry\" id=\"4601\">                            <div style=\"float:left;\"><script type=\"text/javascript\">    /*男女336*280 创建于 2015-02-09*/    var cpro_id = \"u1945933\";</script><script src=\"http://cpro.baidustatic.com/cpro/ui/c.js\" type=\"text/javascript\"></script></div><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height: normal; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt\">	<font size=\"3\"><b style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal\"><span lang=\"ZH-TW\" style=\"font-family: MingLiU; color: black; mso-bidi-font-family: MingLiU\">豪华客房</span></b><b style=\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-family: MingLiU; color: black; mso-bidi-font-family: MingLiU\"><o:p></o:p></span></b></font></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"line-height: normal; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt\">	<span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"color: black\"><o:p><font face=\"宋体, MS Song\" size=\"3\">&nbsp;</font></o:p></span></p><p>	<span lang=\"ZH-TW\" style=\"line-height: 115%; font-family: PMingLiU; color: black; font-size: 11pt; mso-bidi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-fareast-language: ZH-TW; mso-ascii-font-family: Calibri; mso-hansi-font-family: Calibri; mso-ansi-language: EN-US; mso-bidi-language: AR-SA\">在打算到重庆的旅程吗</span><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"line-height: 115%; font-family: Calibri; color: black; font-size: 11pt; mso-bidi-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; mso-fareast-language: ZH-TW; mso-ansi-language: EN-US; mso-bidi-language: AR-SA; mso-fareast-font-family: PMingLiU\"><fon